data.description: Pride of ownership is shown by this owner!  It has been totally remodeled inside and outside. The roofs (main and flat) were replaced March 2018, A/C both in and out have been replaced with a 3.5 ton York in June 2018, Stone w/brick pattern floors replaced in living areas and foyer in 2018, Kitchen remodeled in 2020.  The kitchen is one-of-a-kind and brings you back to Spain with the beautiful tile back splashes. It has wood beamed ceilings, fantastic storage, center island for prep work with seating for two, stainless steel appliances, two built-in beverage coolers in breakfast area, plus it is open to your Florida room or front living room. The carport was converted to a screened porch but can easily be converted back by the next owner.  Can't beat this price for an updated home in town! Remodeled 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath home in Plantation Park.  Large interior lot is fenced in back. Shows beautifully inside.  All major features of the home have been replaced since 2018.  Large 10x10 Shed installed in 2018 in back yard remains.  Kitchen is the heart of the home!
